# Per-milestone working files (D-F4 / D-GITIGNORE).
# Authored during STOP discipline + commit construction; removed before/after commit.
.m*-phase1-stop.md
.m*-recovery.md
.m*-cp5-draft.txt
.m*-checkpoint*.md

# Intentionally untracked (project-specific, do NOT stage):
# - KOAST_METHOD.md           method document, integrated separately
# - KOAST_METHOD_IN_CODE.md   method-in-code document, integrated separately
# - design/logo-concepts*/    unfinished brand exploration; archived when one wins
# These items are NOT pattern-ignored below — they appear in `git status` so
# they remain visible as working files. Listed here to document intent and
# warn against `git add -A` that would sweep them into a commit.

# M5 design archive — scratch / iteration / ui_kits exports kept
# locally for reference but not load-bearing for the chat shell.
# The handoff/, brand/, assets/, fonts/, screenshots/, and root
# CSS files in design/m5-handoff/ ARE tracked.
design/m5-handoff/uploads/
design/m5-handoff/scratch/
design/m5-handoff/ui_kits/
